  <brief_title>Uterine Artery Embolization for Symptomatic Fibroids</brief_title>
  <official_title>Short and Long Term Outcomes of Uterine Artery Embolization.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>University of Manitoba</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>University of Manitoba</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate the safety, efficacy , quality of life and patient satisfaction of
      uterine artery embolization for the treatment of symptomatic uterine fibroids. It will
      provide useful information in the development od guidelines in patient selection, procedural
      management and subsequent follow up.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
